    <item>
      <title>普拉博沃侄子担任财政部长 承诺保持财政连续性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/prabowo-s-nephew-in-finance-ministry-pledges-fiscal-continuity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚新任财政部副部长托马斯·吉万多诺（Thomas Djiwandono，当选总统普拉博沃·苏比安托的侄子）承诺顺利实现财政交接，并保证不会提高债务比率或预算赤字。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/prabowo-s-nephew-in-finance-ministry-pledges-fiscal-continuity</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 08:05:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ION 将于本周完成对意大利 Prelios 15 亿美元的收购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/ion-set-to-close-1-5-billion-deal-for-italy-s-prelios-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过数月与意大利当局就该交易的反复谈判后，ION 集团将于本周尽快完成对资产管理公司 Prelios SpA 的收购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/ion-set-to-close-1-5-billion-deal-for-italy-s-prelios-this-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 08:02:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰开始与债券持有人进行第二轮限制性谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/ukraine-starts-second-round-of-restricted-talks-with-bondholders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，乌克兰一些债券持有人已签署保密协议，开始与政府就重组超过 200 亿美元的债务进行第二轮正式谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/ukraine-starts-second-round-of-restricted-talks-with-bondholders</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 07:53:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国实际工资终于回到金融危机前的峰值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/uk-real-wages-finally-return-to-pre-financial-crisis-peak</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国实际工资终于在近二十年前的金融危机爆发前回到了峰值，这对承诺改善生活水平的基尔·斯塔默（Keir Starmer）领导的新工党政府来说是一个推动力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/uk-real-wages-finally-return-to-pre-financial-crisis-peak</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 07:49:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾将在南海岛屿上建设机场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/philippines-to-develop-airport-in-south-china-sea-island</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在与北京的关系持续紧张之际，菲律宾正在其占领的南海岛屿上修建一座机场，并宣称对这片有争议的海域拥有主权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/philippines-to-develop-airport-in-south-china-sea-island</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 07:11:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
