      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/african-outpost-gets-ready-to-become-world-s-newest-oil-hotspot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在纳米比亚主要港口鲸湾港的繁忙码头上，经济繁荣的种子正在萌芽。]]></description>
